{
  "stem": "5911.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But during the ghetto time, being very, very sick with scarlet fever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] dumping me from one bed to the other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She knew when the German doctors were coming through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because otherwise, I would have been killed right away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a communicable disease.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ongoing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ongoing on any provocation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you walked on the sidewalk, and you were supposed to walk in the ditch.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you walked on the ditch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whatever there was, there were soldiers, there was especially, and Rauck, I remember him, that they picked on whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now then comes-- now, another thing while we were in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They needed-- you see, I'm talking--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in the hospital quite a while--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and I evaded because of my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because remember, scarlet fever, you have things on your neck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I remember being wrapped around-- around the neck and transferred from bed to bed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And don't forget, all the nurses looked after me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then being all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And again, they needed they-- a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They needed a labor camp further out than the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we talk about miracles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Again, a miracle.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's-- I-- my life is full of miracles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'll explain you the miracle what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My mother and my grandmother and my father were shipped out to a labor camp not far from Kovno, because they needed people to build again further down.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember that very vividly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother also going to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I suppose they needed a nurse while the people were working.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "One night will-- one day will always remain in my memory, again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The Jewish people, no matter what, were always singing, try to keep up the morale.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
